OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC rediscovers the case
OL,4,Cfor the BBC
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn 1986 the BBC was under fire as never
OL,7,Fbefore.
OL,9,FIdeologically driven politicians `
OL,10,Fcheered on by certain newspapers ` had
OL,11,Fthe corporation in its sights.
OL,13,FA committee established by the
OL,14,Fgovernment to explore alternatives to
OL,15,Fthe licence fee seemed set to recommend
OL,16,Fadvertising.
OL,18,FAnd the BBC responded with a promotion
OL,19,Fwhich was a work of genius.
OL,21,FWhat did the BBC ever do for us?
OL,23,EPub: 19-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,142,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14102
SC,0002
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F141A1784463086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC rediscovers the case
OL,4,Cfor the BBC
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt featured John Cleese and a host of
OL,7,Fpresenters and stars highlighting the
OL,8,Fdiversity of its output.
OL,10,FA new campaign in the same spirit is
OL,11,Fset to be shown on TV for the first
OL,12,Ftime today. We understand it will debut
OL,13,Fat half time during the World Cup
OL,14,Ffinal.
OL,16,FIt has already appeared online.
OL,18,FThis is exactly what the BBC should be
OL,19,Fdoing.
OL,23,EPub: 19-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,142,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14103
SC,0003
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F141A1784463086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC rediscovers the case
OL,4,Cfor the BBC
OL,5,
OL,6,FThose of us who are passionate in its
OL,7,Fdefence have sometimes felt we were
OL,8,Flosing the propaganda war.
OL,10,FIt somehow didn't matter that 94pc of
OL,11,Fadults use the BBC every week. It was
OL,12,FNetflix this, GB News that.
OL,14,FThere is a principled, even a moral,
OL,15,Fcase for the BBC. We shouldn't be
OL,16,Fashamed to make it.
OL,18,FIt looks as if ITV will soon,
OL,19,Fultimately, be part of an
OL,20,FAmerican-owned organisation.
OL,23,EPub: 19-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,142,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14104
SC,0004
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F141A1784463086
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC rediscovers the case
OL,4,Cfor the BBC
OL,5,
OL,6,FSurely this makes the case for a public
OL,7,Fcorporation free from commercial
OL,8,Finfluence even stronger?
OL,10,FAn organisation whose loyalty is only
OL,11,Fto the public who finance it ` not
OL,12,Fadvertisers, shareholders or corporate
OL,13,Finterests.
OL,15,FAn organisation which appeals to broad
OL,16,Faudiences and serves minorities.
OL,18,FRemember the old mantra ` make the
OL,19,Fpopular good and the good popular.
OL,23,EPub: 19-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,142,140,200,120,0,100
