OL,3,GOPINIONCThe BBC rediscovers the case
OL,4,Cfor the BBC
OL,5,
OL,6,FClearly the TV licence needs to be
OL,7,Freformed or replaced by some kind of
OL,8,Fhousehold levy.
OL,10,FIf our new prime minister clearly
OL,11,Fbelieves that utilities and train
OL,12,Fcompanies are public services which
OL,13,Fshould be in a form of public
OL,14,Fownership, it should be unthinkable to
OL,15,Fallow what is arguably Britain's
OL,16,Fgreatest public service to decline.
OL,23,EPub: 19-Jul-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
